[30;1m3989 | [0m[35mg-paren">(</span><em>length</em><span class="sig-paren">)</span><a class="headerlink" href="#pyxb.bi[0m
[30;1m3990 | [0m[35m<dd><p>Control the maximum encoded size that is checked for XML literal validity.</p>[0m
[30;1m3991 | [0m[35m<p>Python&#8217;s base64 module allows some literals that are invalid[0m
[30;1m3992 | [0m[35maccording to XML rules.  PyXB verifies the validity using a[0m
[30;1m3993 | [0m[35mregular expression, which is costly for something that is[0m
[30;1m3994 | [0m[35munlikely to occur.  Use this function to inhibit checks for[0m
[30;1m3995 | [0m[35mvalidity based on the length of the XML literal.</p>[0m

[30;1m3989 | [0m[35mig-paren">(</span><em>length</em><span class="sig-paren">)</span><a class="headerlink" href="#pyxb.b[0m
[30;1m3990 | [0m[35m<dd><p>Control the maximum encoded size that is checked for XML literal validity.</p>[0m
[30;1m3991 | [0m[35m<p>Python&#8217;s base64 module allows some literals that are invalid[0m
[30;1m3992 | [0m[35maccording to XML rules.  PyXB verifies the validity using a[0m
[30;1m3993 | [0m[35mregular expression, which is costly for something that is[0m
[30;1m3994 | [0m[35munlikely to occur.  Use this function to inhibit checks for[0m
[30;1m3995 | [0m[35mvalidity based on the length of the XML literal.</p>[0m

[30;1m2 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m3 | [0m[35m - Change the element form default to "qualified".  This is necessary[0m
[30;1m4 | [0m[35m   because there is a non-absent target namespace in the schema, and the[0m
[30;1m5 | [0m[35m   documents returned from the service set it as the default namespace.[0m
[30;1m6 | [0m[35m   This causes the XML engine to associate that namespace with[0m
[30;1m7 | [0m[35m   locally-scoped elements like "number", while the "unqualified" form[0m
[30;1m8 | [0m[35m   default caused the schema recorded them as having no namespace.[0m

[30;1m1553 | [0m[35m<dl class="function">[0m
[30;1m1554 | [0m[35m<dt>[0m
[30;1m1555 | [0m[35m<code class="descclassname">pyxb.</code><code class="descname">PreserveInputTimeZone</code><span cla[0m
[30;1m1556 | [0m[35m<dd><p>Control whether time values are converted to UTC during input.</p>[0m
[30;1m1557 | [0m[35m<p>The specification &lt;<a class="reference external" href="http://www.w3.org/TR/xmlschema-2/#dateT[0m

[30;1m572 | [0m[35m        connected components (which can be single nodes).  Appearance[0m
[30;1m573 | [0m[35m        of a node in a set earlier in the list indicates that it has[0m
[30;1m574 | [0m[35m        no dependencies on any node that appears in a subsequent set.[0m
[30;1m575 | [0m[35m        This order is preferred over L{dfsOrder} for code generation,[0m
[30;1m576 | [0m[35m        since it detects loops.[0m

[30;1m590 | [0m[35mion"></span><h3><code class="docutils literal"><span class="pre">--wsdl-location</span></code><a cla[0m
[30;1m591 | [0m[35m<p>Generate bindings for the <code class="docutils literal"><span class="pre">types</span></code> st[0m
[30;1m592 | [0m[35mThis option is equivalent to retrieving the WSDL, extracting the schema[0m
